konsole-tray (0.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix raising the wrong window/tab when several Konsole windows run in one
    process and their active tabs share a generic session name (most visible
    with multiple "claude" tabs). Disambiguate windows by their specific
    displayed title rather than the generic NameRole, and match the most
    specific candidate across all windows before any less specific one.

